Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.45,0:00:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.46,0:00:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔比斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.68,0:00:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁  接下来拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.39,0:00:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.61,0:00:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借这个  希望你能保护这个岛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能办得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.38,0:00:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能办得到的只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.54,0:00:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的能办到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.05,0:00:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔精灵号  出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.89,0:02:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔精灵号  着陆确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.77,0:02:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲板解除  现在起精灵号…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.37,0:02:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知～生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.44,0:02:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.92,0:02:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地形显示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法弗尼尔的所在方位图
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.25,0:03:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…那是  敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.89,0:03:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.54,0:03:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回答  会被他侵蚀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.26,0:03:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.30,0:03:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.66,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回答了  人类就会毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.84,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体…不能随心所欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.15,0:03:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受法弗尼尔的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和它一体化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码已经解除了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.26,0:04:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在能使用的只有「电磁枪」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.71,0:04:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即转移去林多布姆的发射台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.28,0:04:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以利用武岛的滑行跑道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里直接袭击他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.78,0:04:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在林多布姆的发射台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.94,0:04:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射是无法在这里控制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.99,0:04:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.02,0:04:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.86,0:04:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  他打算同化你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避开他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.72,0:04:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.97,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接系统启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左臂解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.22,0:05:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  你的模拟体突然被切断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.38,0:05:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快摆脱他  一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑  用电磁枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.26,0:05:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还无法接上法弗尼尔的回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须一招制胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.98,0:05:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.63,0:05:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.62,0:05:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑  抓住电磁枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标  完全消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员存活确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.53,0:06:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收驾驶舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告各部门损失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.77,0:06:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.91,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.42,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭树岛的空中设施60%受损
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.91,0:06:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武岛滑行跑道一部分受损  第二跑道被毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损失惨重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤亡情况呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房屋被毁13处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前失踪人员28名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有两人确认生还
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向岛迎击系统完全被毁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真的是我们的岛屿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.32,0:06:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.16,0:06:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲好像是牺牲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于真壁代指挥官的策略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.00,0:07:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.00,0:07:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为那是当时的最佳选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.04,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.03,0:07:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果由你指挥的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.17,0:07:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有兴趣谈论假设的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.35,0:07:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您今后有何打算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.06,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算留在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞  敌人的分析工作还没完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的情况如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.74,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.92,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就能预见会这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  今晚要好好休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.33,0:08:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.59,0:08:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.20,0:09:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  原来有这样的地方啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.85,0:09:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家后问你的爸爸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他都知道  爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.27,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.04,0:09:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有很多伤员呢  快回去快回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.94,0:09:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.49,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多保重身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以通知真壁叔叔吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.19,0:09:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  多给我一点时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.76,0:09:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.55,0:09:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.79,0:09:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受伤没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.76,0:10:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春日井  那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.82,0:10:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  羽佐间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.45,0:10:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天能来学校吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.06,0:10:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我一定去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快进屋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.11,0:10:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  真矢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.55,0:10:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.41,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  今晚要好好休息哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.89,0:10:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们俩  晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.56,0:11:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  你在干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏得你能平安无事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西从哪儿捡来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.90,0:11:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌  这是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.17,0:11:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家…在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  小藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.37,0:12:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灯也不开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.32,0:12:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.63,0:12:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸  你爸爸他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.45,0:12:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.05,0:12:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.98,0:13:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐那东西感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.35,0:13:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.95,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吃惊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的人们做了这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.83,0:13:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.57,0:13:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么对于日本已经不存在的事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是29年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京呢  大阪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.55,0:13:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早之前已经消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.06,0:13:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙宫岛已经先从地图上消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.19,0:13:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.12,0:13:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西竟然存在于现实中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是真实的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.98,0:13:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到昨天  只有这个岛屿才是乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能得救是多亏了校长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.20,0:14:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是多亏了总士的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙还会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.36,0:14:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会和我一起战斗吧  一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  特地让您来一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.11,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于一骑的身体状况  我有话对您说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.64,0:15:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.06,0:15:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  因为职员会议回来晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算继续说谎吗  姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.18,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非  你在生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.75,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.31,0:15:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服是远见医生给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.90,0:15:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.02,0:15:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你今天不会回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.75,0:15:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能不回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不在  饭都没人做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.59,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸以前也是经常做饭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.14,0:16:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是结婚前的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走开  今天我来做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不回家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.10,0:16:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.18,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西今天已经没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这里让我感觉更冷静一些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.22,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于刚才的是事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如果我来指挥」那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.45,0:16:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我  会做得更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.13,0:16:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信那就是他派你去CDC的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.74,0:16:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原指挥官皆城先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.44,0:17:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  好吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这米没淘过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.20,0:17:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.51,0:17:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.23,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.00,0:17:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.72,0:17:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上的事情你都知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.63,0:17:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别问我「为什么瞒着」啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.38,0:17:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定和总士一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.92,0:17:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见医生说过吧  快点睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要开始驾驶法弗尼尔的训练了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.99,0:18:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.65,0:18:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于一骑的身体状况  我有话对您说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.34,0:18:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭乘时  发现他的意识与平时有所不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.62,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且发现战斗后  染色体发生了变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.13,0:18:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前不加以观察尚不能断定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.05,0:18:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红音  对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.24,0:19:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.03,0:19:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  藏前是机器人驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没有一起避难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.64,0:19:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏前参加战斗了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.27,0:19:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  爸爸没有告诉我那些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机器人  我也能驾驶吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当真吗  说不定会死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.29,0:19:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一骑驾驶了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城和一骑最近好像常在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.78,0:19:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想一起去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.23,0:19:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哪一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.37,0:20:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很努力呢  一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.87,0:20:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  把衣服都脱掉到这儿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  全部？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在后面的机器里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的时候就洗好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.18,0:20:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  就这样正面朝着这里走过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  从这里是看不见的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.93,0:20:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会很痛吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.52,0:20:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  穿上防护服就不会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.75,0:20:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防护服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.17,0:21:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COSPLAY？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是很痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他那件事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗  皆城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.18,0:21:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶系统已经把上次的战斗数据转移过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.48,0:21:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下次战斗时就会轻松一些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.85,0:21:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  开始精灵号的战斗系统测试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.73,0:21:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齐格菲系统  启动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.43,0:22:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当人们了解一切时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.41,0:22:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会知道世界的尽头  能力的极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.65,0:22:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会明白梦终有一天会醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.04,0:22:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们相信我们能超越这一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.36,0:22:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此时

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.01,0:23:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.38,0:23:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是迷惘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.37,0:23:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是欢欣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.87,0:23:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有不知所措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.84,0:23:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩一起  一定能飞翔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.44,0:23:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上升吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.48,0:23:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.28,0:23:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本不想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  苍穹的Fafnir  第三话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.38,0:23:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷宫 真相


